!! Chat Widget

The `chat` widget is to chat with Anything LLM.

!! Syntax

```
<$chat workspace="space" thread="">>
```


!! Content and attributes
|!Attributes |!Type |!Description |
|workspace |required|The `workspace` slug name in Anything LLM |
|thread |optional|The `thread` slug name in Anything LLM. If missing, the `default` thread will be used |

!! Example


<$macrocall $name="wikitext-example" 
src="""<$chat workspace="test"/>"""/>

